Thanks for testing out this early build!
Since the app is still in its Beta phase, you might run into a few bugs
or rough edges. Your feedback is exactly what we need to iron out the issues, add new features,
and make these tweaks as powerful as possible. If you run into any problems or have a suggestion, please let us know!

